 CHVRCHES 的劳伦·梅伯里 (Lauren Mayberry) 凭借钢琴民谣《Are You Awake?》首次独唱https://www.nme.com/news/music/chvrches-lauren-mayberry-makes-solo-debut-with-piano-ballad-are-you-awake-3491767?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=chvrches-lauren-梅伯里与钢琴民谣首秀独奏，你醒了吗David James YoungThu, 31 Aug 2023 23:17:52 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndiePophttps://www.nme.com/?p=3491767 <p><img width="1999" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Lauren-Mayberry-Scarlett-Casciello.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Lauren-Mayberry-Scarlett-Casciello.jpg 1999w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Lauren-Mayberry-Scarlett-Casciello-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Lauren-Mayberry-Scarlett-Casciello-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Lauren-Mayberry-Scarlett-Casciello-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Lauren-Mayberry-Scarlett-Casciello-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Lauren-Mayberry-Scarlett-Casciello-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1999px) 100vw, 1999px" /></p><p> “对孤独和思乡的思考很多”激发了主唱的第一首个人歌曲</p><p>后<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chvrches-lauren-mayberry-makes-solo-debut-with-piano-ballad-are-you-awake-3491767">CHVRCHES 的劳伦·梅伯里 (Lauren Mayberry) 凭借钢琴民谣《Are You Awake?》首次独唱。</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="1999" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Lauren-Mayberry-Scarlett-Casciello.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Lauren-Mayberry-Scarlett-Casciello.jpg 1999w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Lauren-Mayberry-Scarlett-Casciello-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Lauren-Mayberry-Scarlett-Casciello-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Lauren-Mayberry-Scarlett-Casciello-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Lauren-Mayberry-Scarlett-Casciello-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Lauren-Mayberry-Scarlett-Casciello-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1999px) 100vw, 1999px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chvrches">CHVRCHES</a>主唱劳伦<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lauren-mayberry">·梅伯里 (Lauren Mayberry)</a>正式发行了她作为独奏艺术家的首张单曲：一首鲜明、亲密的钢琴驱动民谣，名为“Are You Awake？”</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/chvrches-mad-cool-2022-karaoke-bangers-robert-smith-decade-together-3264219">Chvrches at Mad Cool 2022 卡拉 OK 歌曲、Robert Smith 和十年的合作</a></strong></li></ul><p>梅伯里与加拿大歌手兼作曲家小托比亚斯·杰索<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tobias-jesso-jr">(Tobias Jesso Jr)</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zedd">Zedd 的</a>合作者马修·科马 (Matthew Koma) 合作创作了这首歌，马修·科马也担任这首歌的制作人。在该单曲发行之前，梅伯里宣布了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chvrches-lauren-mayberry-launches-fun-freaky-sad-weird-joyful-solo-career-with-tour-3471192">她的首次个人巡演</a>，并用 30 秒的预览<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chvrches-lauren-mayberry-previews-debut-solo-single-are-you-awake-3483022">预告了这首单曲</a>。当时，她在社交媒体上分享说，当谈到即将到来的个人首秀时，她“在兴奋和极度恐惧之间摇摆不定”。</p><p>根据梅伯里的新闻声明，“你醒了吗？”她和杰索在一次写作会议上走到了一起，她最初全神贯注于“思考很多关于孤独和思乡的事情”。</p><p> “托比亚斯一开始演奏和弦，我很快就想到了歌词和旋律，”她说。 “我和马修一起完成了这首歌，他真正理解我想说的内容。”</p><p>听听《你醒了吗？》以下： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="你醒着么？" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zMhnoRR935o?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>梅伯里接着指出，单飞生涯，更不用说在 CHVRCHES 提供的直接框架之外制作任何音乐，最初是她“无法想象的”。然而，当她意识到“[她]需要写的一些东西必须纯粹从[她]自己的观点来完成时，这种情况最终发生了变化。”</p><p> “我从来没有真正想过我会写一首钢琴民谣，或者一张个人专辑句号，所以生活真的充满了惊喜，”她说。 “我真的很期待这一章，迫不及待地想让人们听到更多的音乐。”</p><p>在《你醒着吗？》发行之前梅伯里的个人作品很少。她为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/death-cab-for-cutie">Death Cab for Cutie 的</a>歌曲《Northern Lights》客串演唱，该歌曲收录在他们 2018 年专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/death-cab-cutie-thank-today-album-review-2366912">《Thank You For Today》</a>中。</p><p>她还与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">The National</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/aaron-dessner">Aaron Dessner</a>合作翻唱了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frightened-rabbit">Frightened Rabbit</a>的“Who&#39;d Kill You Now?”为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/death-cab-for-cutie-ben-gibbard-reflects-tribute-show-frightened-rabbit-scott-hutchison-rough-trade-nyc-2417398">乐队已故主唱</a>斯科特·哈钦森 (Scott Hutchinson) 制作的纪念专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/various-artists-tiny-changes-a-celebration-of-frightened-rabbits-the-midnight-organ-fight-2526196">《Tiny Changes》</a> 。</p><p> CHVRCHES 最近的录音室专辑是 2021 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/chvrches-screen-violence-review-3029924">《Screen Violence》</a> 。苏格兰合成流行音乐三重奏目前正准备发行他们首张录音室专辑 2013 年的《The Bones Of What You Believe》的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chvrches-share-unheard-song-manhattan-announce-10th-anniversary-bones-of-what-you-believe-3483993">10 周年纪念再版</a>。新版本包括四首前所未闻的歌曲和五首 2013 年的现场录音，将于 10 月 13 日发行。</p><p>后<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chvrches-lauren-mayberry-makes-solo-debut-with-piano-ballad-are-you-awake-3491767">CHVRCHES 的劳伦·梅伯里 (Lauren Mayberry) 凭借钢琴民谣《Are You Awake?》首次独唱。</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
